q \in \mathbb{N}^{\ge 2}
q
 P(q) =  \begin{cases}   1 + 2 \sum_{i = 1}^{\lceil q / 2 \rceil - 1} x^i + x^{q / 2} & \text{if $q$ is even}, \\   1 + 2 \sum_{i = 1}^{\lceil q / 2 \rceil - 1} x^i & \text{else.} \end{cases} 
q
P(q)^n
